
For cable-based serial port communication to the Creates from a Mac, you will need to install drivers.

For the StarTech serial port cable
     Install the driver for Prolific/PL2303X/MacOSX10.6/ from the CD in the box

For the turtlebot USB-Create cable
    Go to http://www.ftdichip.com/Drivers/VCP.htm
    Install the 64 bit OSX driver.

